author: Nick Crowley
description:
Throughout television history, there have been countless instances of disturbing moments and accidents captured when the cameras are live. These are just a few of the darkest moments in television history.

MUSIC USED: 
After Hours by Repulsive - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dS9nqT6_ph4&list=RDdS9nqT6_ph4&start_radio=1 
LOSTLOSTLOST by Repulsive - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KdnNrc4aIiA&list=RDKdnNrc4aIiA&start_radio=1 
Traces of Something Left Behind [untitled vi] by Repulsive - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cORomeR16Sg 
Many songs by Audible Dread - https://audible-dread.itch.io/ 

Topics Include: Missing girl found in river on live TV, The Eriksson Twins (Sabina and Ursula Eriksson), SuperTalent Murder (Roman Brnada), Gardener’s World Murder (Rod and Rachel Saunders) 

CHAPTERS: 
0:00 - The River
4:19 - The Eriksson Twins 
16:05 - SuperTalent [Roman Brnada] 
25:41 - Gardener’s World [Rod & Rachel Saunders]
